('743','COM_AKEEBA_CONFIG_POSTPROCFTP_HOST_DESCRIPTION','FTP server\'s host name, without the protocol. This means that <tt>ftp://example.com</tt> is <b>invalid</b> and <tt>example.com</tt> is valid. This engine only supports FTP and FTPS servers. It <u>does not</u> support SFTP, SCP and other SSH variants.','/home/indicoweb/public_html/demo/iks/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.com_akeeba.ini'),
