('2726','COM_CPANEL_MSG_HTACCESS_BODY','A change to the default .htaccess and web.config files was made in Joomla! 3.4 to disallow folder listings by default.  Users are recommended to implement this change in their files.  Please see <a href="https://docs.joomla.org/Special:MyLanguage/Preconfigured_htaccess">this page</a> for more information.','/home/indicoweb/public_html/demo/iks/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.com_cpanel.ini'),
