('8817','PLG_SAMPLEDATA_BLOG_OVERVIEW_DESC','Sample data which will set up a blog site.<br>If the site is multilingual, the data will be tagged to the active backend language.','/home/indicoweb/public_html/demo/iks/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_sampledata_blog.ini'),
